OL,3,CWales beaten 4-2 by Belgium as World
OL,4,CCup hopes suffer hammer blow
OL,6,FWales' hopes of automatic
OL,7,Fqualification for next year's World
OL,8,FCup are hanging by a thread after a 4-
OL,9,F2 defeat to Belgium in Cardiff.
OL,11,FThe mood in Welsh football was a glum
OL,12,Fone following a dismal 3-0 defeat to
OL,13,FEngland last Thursday evening.
OL,15,FBut it was improved dramatically 24
OL,16,Fhours later when Belgium were held to
OL,17,Fa 0-0 by North Macedonia, blowing
OL,18,FGroup J wide open and putting Wales'
OL,19,FWorld Cup fate back in their own hands.
