OL,3,CWales beaten 4-2 by Belgium as World
OL,4,CCup hopes suffer hammer blow
OL,6,FJoe Rodon was completely unmarked six
OL,7,Fyards out when he rose to meet Sorba
OL,8,FThomas' corner. His downward header
OL,9,Fbounced into the roof of Thibaut
OL,10,FCourtois' net. The roof of the Cardiff
OL,11,FCity Stadium ended up somewhere in the
OL,12,FRiver Taff.
OL,14,FAfter 10 minutes, things could not
OL,15,Fhave been going any better, but this
OL,16,Fwas never going to be easy.
