OL,3,CWales beaten 4-2 by Belgium as World
OL,4,CCup hopes suffer hammer blow
OL,6,FBefore the half hour mark, things got
OL,7,Fworse. Jeremy Doku made something out
OL,8,Fof a seemingly wasteful long ball to
OL,9,Fthe far corner. Thomas couldn't
OL,10,Frecover in time and the cutback found
OL,11,FThomas Muenier, who blasted the ball
OL,12,Fbeyond Darlow, who may feel like he
OL,13,Fshould have done better.
OL,15,FA silence befell the Welsh capital.
