OL,3,CWales beaten 4-2 by Belgium as World
OL,4,CCup hopes suffer hammer blow
OL,6,FSuddenly Wales looked out of sorts and
OL,7,FDoku was causing problems down the
OL,8,Fright hand side. The winger's cross
OL,9,Ffound an onrushing Leandro Trossard
OL,10,Fand collective hearts sank. But
OL,11,FRodon's recovering block sent the ball
OL,12,Fspinning into the safety of the Canton
OL,13,FStand.
OL,15,FAs the game raced towards half time,
OL,16,FDe Bruyne - of all people - saw his
OL,17,Feffort from inside the box land in the
OL,18,Fcar park.
