OL,3,CWales beaten 4-2 by Belgium as World
OL,4,CCup hopes suffer hammer blow
OL,6,FThe opening exchanges of the second
OL,7,Fhalf were the quietest of the match so
OL,8,Ffar. Wales probed and prodded but
OL,9,Fthere was nothing of real substance
OL,10,Finterest Courtois.
OL,12,FIf the first half had been a street
OL,13,Fbrawl, the second had been a
OL,14,Fpillowfight. The 75th minute brought a
OL,15,Fgift for the visitors.
OL,17,FWales were slow to react to a slack
OL,18,Fbackpass that had forced Darlow into a
OL,19,Fweak headed clearance.
