OL,3,CWales beaten 4-2 by Belgium as World
OL,4,CCup hopes suffer hammer blow
OL,6,FTrossard poked the ball harmlessly in
OL,7,Fthe box and James inexplicably threw
OL,8,Fhis arm at it. There was no debating
OL,9,Fthis spot kick. Darlow guessed tight
OL,10,Fthis time but De Bruyne was too
OL,11,Faccurate. 3-1. Hope fades.
OL,13,FBut these two teams don't do anything
OL,14,Fby halves - there were seven goals in
OL,15,Fthe reverse fixture.
